PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (DOGRIB SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT, NORTH SLAVE REGION, N.W.T.) which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of land in the Northwest Territory, until September 30, 2001, and (b) repeals the Withdrawal from Disposal of Certain Lands Order (North Slave Region, N.W.T.), made by Order in Council P.C. 1997-595.
